      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 leading-tight">Open specifications for the feed ecosystem</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">Feeds power the open web — RSS, Atom, JSON Feed, AT Protocol — but the infrastructure around them has gaps. feedspec.org publishes open specs to fill them.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Built on standards you already use. Non-breaking extensions that degrade gracefully. Developed in the open.</p>
